      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * University of Edinburgh</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg/330px-Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg/500px-Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4a/Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Informatics_Forum_-_geograph.org.uk_-_929224.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Informatics_Forum\">Informatics Forum</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p>The <b>University of Edinburgh</b>, <br />\nin <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edinburgh\">Edinburgh</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scotland\">Scotland</a>, is one of Scotland's ancient universities, founded in 1582. The <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Research_Excellence_Framework\">Research Excellence Framework</a>, a research ranking used by the UK government to determine future research funding, ranked Edinburgh 4th in the UK for research power, with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Edinburgh_School_of_Informatics\">Computer Science and Informatics</a> ranking 1st in the UK <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">Donald Michie</a> was head of the University of Edinburgh's Department of Machine Intelligence from 1965 until 1985 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> , when he left to found the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turing_Institute\">Turing Institute</a> in  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glasgow\">Glasgow</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Edinburgh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ioannis_Antonoglou\" title=\"Ioannis Antonoglou\">Ioannis Antonoglou</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#DBasin\" title=\"Mathematician\">David Basin</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#ABundy\" title=\"Mathematician\">Alan Bundy</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Christopher_Clark\" title=\"Christopher Clark\">Christopher Clark</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kevin_Coplan\" title=\"Kevin Coplan\">Kevin Coplan</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Peter_Dayan\" title=\"Peter Dayan\">Peter Dayan</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jim_Doran\" title=\"Jim Doran\">Jim Doran</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Maarten_van_Emden\" title=\"Maarten van Emden\">Maarten van Emden</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ian_Frank\" title=\"Ian Frank\">Ian Frank</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alejandro_Gonz%C3%A1lez_Romero\" title=\"Alejandro González Romero\">Alejandro González Romero</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jean_Hayes_Michie\" title=\"Jean Hayes Michie\">Jean Hayes Michie</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Eduardo_F._Morales\" title=\"Eduardo F. Morales\">Eduardo F. Morales</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Danny_Kopec\" title=\"Danny Kopec\">Danny Kopec</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/David_Levy\" title=\"David Levy\">David Levy</a>, associated </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">Donald Michie</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Stephen_Muggleton\" title=\"Stephen Muggleton\">Stephen Muggleton</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tim_Niblett\" title=\"Tim Niblett\">Tim Niblett</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gordon_Plotkin\">Gordon Plotkin</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fred_Popowich\" title=\"Fred Popowich\">Fred Popowich</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alen_Shapiro\" title=\"Alen Shapiro\">Alen Shapiro</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Amos_Storkey\" title=\"Amos Storkey\">Amos Storkey</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Soei_Tan\" title=\"Soei Tan\">Soei Tan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Austin_Tate\">Austin Tate</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chris_J._Thornton\" title=\"Chris J. Thornton\">Chris J. Thornton</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Greg_Wilson\" title=\"Greg Wilson\">Greg Wilson</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Zdenek_Zdrahal\" title=\"Zdenek Zdrahal\">Zdenek Zdrahal</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Programs\">Chess Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Edinburgh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Moby\" title=\"Moby\">Moby</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Edinburgh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Edinburgh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Edinburgh\">University of Edinburgh from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Edinburgh_School_of_Informatics\">University of Edinburgh School of Informatics from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ed.ac.uk/\">University of Edinburgh Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/%7Eshm/MI/mi.html\">The Machine Intelligence series</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.inf.ed.ac.uk/about/AIhistory.html\">Artificial Intelligence at Edinburgh University&#160;: a Perspective</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.inf.ed.ac.uk/infweb/student-services/ito/admin/jim-howe\">Jim Howe</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Edinburgh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Informatics_Forum\">Informatics Forum</a>, a new university building on what was for decades a car park in a gap site. Covers a whole block. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edinburgh_Central_Mosque\">Edinburgh Central Mosque</a> in the background, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.geograph.org.uk/profile/196\">Richard Webb</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.geograph.org.uk/photo/929224\">Informatics Forum (C) Richard Webb&#160;:: Geograph Britain and Ireland</a>, August 17, 2008, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/deed.en\">CC BY-SA 2.0</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ed.ac.uk/informatics/about/location/forum\">The Forum | The University of Edinburgh</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Edinburgh\">University of Edinburgh from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Edinburgh\">University of Edinburgh from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.inf.ed.ac.uk/about/AIhistory.html\">Artificial Intelligence at Edinburgh University&#160;: a Perspective</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.inf.ed.ac.uk/infweb/student-services/ito/admin/jim-howe\">Jim Howe</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.turingarchive.org/trust/\">Turing Trust - Historical Note</a> by Donald Michie: \"In association with the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Strathclyde\">University of Strathclyde</a>, the Turing Institute hosted seven public lectures in the period 1985-93\"</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301010651\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.666 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion